title: 820-4924 no PP3V3_S5
message:
I have a board 820-4924 no power, consuming 0.01A
PPBUS_G3H = 12.56v
PP5V_S5 = 5v
PP3V3_S5 = 0V

title: 820-4924 no PP3V3_S5
message: Post basic voltages of U7501; pins 23, 12, 13, 22, 29, 21.

title: 820-4924 no PP3V3_S5
message:
U7501; 
pins 23 PPVIN_S5_HS_OTHER3V3 12.56
12 SMC_PM_G2_EN 3.3v
13 P5VP3V3_VREF2 1.9v
22 P5VP3V3_VREG3 3.2v
29 PP5V_S5 5.0v
21 S5_PWR_EN 3.4 v

already replaced u7501 and  q7560

title: 820-4924 no PP3V3_S5
message:
Replaced why?
Please post all the steps you did in a repair process; including the reason of a component change...

With these voltages, U7501 MUST generate 3V3_S5, at L7560.
If not, check all surrounded components and their traces.
Be sure to have good solders.
Also check diode mode at L7520/60.

title: 820-4924 no PP3V3_S5
message:
ok, C3208 was shorted i found L7560 shorted into ground on diode mode. 
thanks for your help
